pages.text:
Host Your Next Event With Us!
Join us at Hank’s Hair of the Dog Saloon for your next event in paradise. Whether you are looking to celebrate a birthday, corporate event, or planning your dream wedding in the Keys, our unique outdoor spaces and original menus will make your special day unforgettable! Available for holiday gatherings, corporate functions, private, semi-private events and all your event needs!
Contact us today at
hanksandgarbosevents@gmail.com
or clicking the button below to email us.
Book Your Event Today
Private Event Spaces
Front Courtyard
Our exclusive Courtyard is the perfect location for your next event! This charming space will provide the perfect tropical, Key West atmosphere for you and your guests. Private bar & catering options available to fit any occasion.
Perfect for 125 guests
Stage available for live music
Great for a casual cocktail party or a formal event
Hanging lights to illuminate any evening
soiree
Includes: A
private space for your guests, set up &
breakdown of event.*
Please contact us for pricing and more details.
*Additional fees for food & beverage, private bartender, staff gratuity and sales tax vary by event.
Contact Us For More Details
Back Courtyard
Our Back Patio area is the perfect spot for your next private or semi-private event. It’s like a party in your own backyard, if your backyard were in the heart of downtown Key West! You will enjoy a charming space dedicated to your group with the option of a private bar and catering.
Ideal for up to 60 guests
Shaded for afternoon events & hanging lights for evenings
Includes:
The set up &
breakdown of event.*
Please contact us for pricing and more details.
*Additional fees for food & beverage, private bartender, staff gratuity and sales tax vary by event.
Contact Us For More Details
Open Bar Brands
Call Open Bar
Stoli, Bacardi, Captain Morgan, Jack Daniels, Milagro Tequila, Tanqueray Gin, Domestic Beer, House Wine and Soft Drinks
Premium Open Bar
Grey Goose, Papas Pilar Gold, Jameson, Patron Tequila, Bombay Sapphire, all Beer, Wine and Soft Drinks.
Ask about our consumption bar options, or drink ticket options as well!
Catering Options
Enjoy Key West’s favorite food truck at your next event!
Ask about our consumption-based food packages.
• Cheese & Fruit Platters available – perfect for Cocktail Hour!
• Have your very own gourmet Taco Station.
• Buffet options available.
Contact us with event details for pricing!
